PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE INCOME TAX REGULATIONS which extend the definition of "qualifying property", as it applies to a "Pooled Trust Fund", to include any property that is convertible into shares or is exchangeable therefor, or that confers a right to acquire shares.
